14:22.523 --> 14:24.858
AS SOON AS SHE WALK
THROUGH THAT DOOR, YOU POP HER.

14:24.858 --> 14:26.927
YOU HEAR ME?
I WANT HER DEAD.

14:26.927 --> 14:29.195
YOU HEAR ME, HORSE?

14:29.195 --> 14:31.131
WHO YOU TALKING ABOUT?

14:31.131 --> 14:33.099
‐I DON'T KNOW.
‐OH, OKAY.

14:33.099 --> 14:35.101
SO I'M GONNA LET "Q" KNOW
YOU THINK YOU THE BOSS

14:35.101 --> 14:36.369
SINCE HE BEEN GONE.

14:36.369 --> 14:38.471
‐COME ON, MAN.
‐TELL ME.

14:38.471 --> 14:40.006
WHAT'S HORSE UP TO,

14:40.006 --> 14:42.543
AND WHAT IT GO TO DO
WITH WHAT'S ON THE TV?

14:42.543 --> 14:43.977
HE GETTING READY
TO POP THAT LAWYER.

14:43.977 --> 14:45.211
WHAT LAWYER?

14:45.211 --> 14:46.880
YEAH, THE ONE
HELPED YOUR BIGGER BROTHER.

14:46.880 --> 14:48.715
AND I SURE MISSED ‐‐
‐HEY, FOOL,

14:48.715 --> 14:50.150
FINISH WHAT YOU WAS SAYING.

14:50.150 --> 14:52.018
HORSE FINNA TO TAKE OUT
VERONICA HARRINGTON?

14:52.018 --> 14:54.087
‐YEAH.
‐WHERE HE AT?

14:54.087 --> 14:55.522
HE AT THE HOUSE
RIGHT NOW WAITING ON HER

14:55.522 --> 14:56.557
TO WALK THROUGH THAT DOOR.

14:56.557 --> 15:00.026
‐WHO SET THAT UP?
‐THAT THERE JUDGE ON TV.

15:00.026 --> 15:02.703
THE HELL?
COLD BLOODED.

15:02.703 --> 15:04.971
LOOK, I NEED TO FIND "Q."

15:04.971 --> 15:08.208
LIKE, I SAID, SHORTY,
WE DON'T KNOW WHERE HE AT.

15:08.208 --> 15:09.943
GET ON THAT GAME.
LET'S GO.

15:09.943 --> 15:11.512
EXCUSE ME.

15:19.352 --> 15:21.187
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

15:25.258 --> 15:26.359
Benny:
OPEN THE DOOR.

15:32.165 --> 15:35.435
MAMA, OPEN THE DOOR.

15:42.976 --> 15:44.878
BENJAMIN.

15:44.878 --> 15:46.312
HOW'D YOU FIND ME?

15:46.312 --> 15:50.383
THERE'S ONLY A FEW PLACES
AROUND HERE YOU CAN AFFORD.

15:50.383 --> 15:53.186
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

15:53.186 --> 15:54.454
I CAME HERE TO GET YOU.

15:54.454 --> 15:56.356
WELL, YOU COULDN'T HAVE
COME HERE FOR THAT.

15:56.356 --> 15:58.224
‐MOM.
‐I'M FINE.

15:58.224 --> 15:59.826
NO, YOU'RE NOT ‐‐
YOU GOT ENOUGH MONEY

15:59.826 --> 16:02.435
FOR A FEW NIGHTS
AT THIS PLACE.

16:02.435 --> 16:04.137
WELL, I GET PAID SOON.

16:04.137 --> 16:06.907
AND I'LL HAVE ENOUGH
TO BUY SOME MORE TIME.

16:06.907 --> 16:08.141
THEN I'LL GO TO WORK
TOMORROW.

16:08.141 --> 16:10.143
AND I'LL HAVE ENOUGH
TO BUY ANOTHER NIGHT.

16:10.143 --> 16:12.212
MOM, COME HOME.

16:12.212 --> 16:15.215
MY HOME BURNED DOWN,
BENJAMIN.

16:15.215 --> 16:16.617
MOM.

16:16.617 --> 16:18.819
I DON'T WANT TO TALK ABOUT THIS
IN FRONT OF THIS BABY.

16:20.821 --> 16:22.288
QUINCY.

16:22.288 --> 16:24.190
‐DON'T YOU WAKE THAT BABY UP.
‐HE CAN'T EVEN HEAR US.

16:24.190 --> 16:27.360
HE'S ASLEEP.

16:27.360 --> 16:29.930
GO HOME, BENJAMIN.

16:29.930 --> 16:32.065
GO ON.
‐NO, NO.

16:32.065 --> 16:34.100
NOT UNTIL I SAY
WHAT I CAME HERE TO SAY.

16:37.270 --> 16:38.271
MEAN IT.

16:38.271 --> 16:42.142
I MEAN IT.

16:44.210 --> 16:45.979
I'VE BEEN TO FOUR
DIFFERENT HOTELS

16:45.979 --> 16:47.981
FLIRTING WITH FOUR DIFFERENT
DESK CLERKS

16:47.981 --> 16:50.584
AND ONE WITH NO TEETH.

16:50.584 --> 16:52.152
SO YOU GONNA TALK TO ME.

16:52.152 --> 16:53.920
SO YOU WANT TO MAKE JOKES?

16:53.920 --> 16:55.722
I'M NOT JOKING.

16:55.722 --> 16:58.024
IF YOU WAKE UP THIS BABY...

17:00.426 --> 17:03.670
NO ONE LOVES YOU LIKE I DO.

17:03.670 --> 17:05.806
SO YOU LIED TO ME.

17:05.806 --> 17:07.240
YEAH.

17:07.240 --> 17:09.409
I LOVE YOU,
SO I LIED TO YOU?

17:09.409 --> 17:10.644
NO.

17:10.644 --> 17:13.179
I DIDN'T TELL YOU THE TRUTH
BECAUSE I WAS ‐‐

17:13.179 --> 17:14.981
I WAS TRYING TO PROTECT YOU.

17:14.981 --> 17:19.419
BENJAMIN, YOU CAN'T PROTECT ME
BEHIND A LIE.

17:19.419 --> 17:23.389
YOU DIDN'T TELL ME
TONY WAS MY DADDY.

17:23.389 --> 17:24.858
THAT WASN'T A LIE.

17:24.858 --> 17:26.459
WELL, THEN WHAT WAS IT?

17:26.459 --> 17:28.929
I JUST DIDN'T TELL YOU.
THAT'S ALL.

17:28.929 --> 17:31.932
BECAUSE
YOU WERE PROTECTING ME.

17:31.932 --> 17:34.200
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

17:34.200 --> 17:36.670
CAN'T SAY NOTHING
NOW BECAUSE I BUSTED YOU.

17:37.604 --> 17:39.439
[ SIGHS ]

17:39.439 --> 17:43.577
OKAY.
LOOK, I, UH, I LOVE YOU.

17:43.577 --> 17:44.778
AND CANDACE LOVES YOU.

17:44.778 --> 17:46.647
OH, BOY, PLEASE.

17:46.647 --> 17:48.181
SHE DOES.

17:48.181 --> 17:50.216
IF SHE DIDN'T, SHE WOULDN'T HAVE
HAD THAT ERICA GIRL

17:50.216 --> 17:53.153
SEND ME THE CAR
FOR $500 FOR YOU.

17:53.153 --> 17:55.488
I DON'T BIT MORE
BELIEVE THAT.

17:55.488 --> 17:57.190
MOM, CANDACE IS ‐‐

17:57.190 --> 17:59.993
STOP MENTIONING HER NAME.

17:59.993 --> 18:01.034
THAT'S YOUR CHILD.

18:01.034 --> 18:02.102
BENJAMIN.

18:02.102 --> 18:04.871
FINE, LET'S NOT TALK
ABOUT HER, OKAY?

18:04.871 --> 18:07.040
LET'S TALK ABOUT ME.

18:07.040 --> 18:08.775
MOMMY, I LOVE YOU.

18:08.775 --> 18:11.477
I WOULD NEVER, KNOWINGLY,
PUT YOU IN HARM'S WAY.

18:11.477 --> 18:16.683
THAT GIRL TRICKED YOU
INTO MORTGAGING MY HOME.

18:16.683 --> 18:18.418
THAT IS HARM'S WAY.

18:18.418 --> 18:20.654
THAT MEANS SHE GOT THE MONEY
TO PAY FOR IT, DIDN'T SHE?

18:20.654 --> 18:23.489
YES.
AND HOW DID SHE?

18:23.489 --> 18:25.458
I DON'T KNOW.
BUT SHE GOT IT.

18:25.458 --> 18:29.362
HOW DID SHE GET MILLIONS
OF DOLLARS, BENJAMIN?

18:29.362 --> 18:31.131
I DON'T KNOW.

18:31.131 --> 18:32.933
BUT THE TOW YARD IS MINE.
IT'S PAID FOR.

18:32.933 --> 18:35.536
AND IT'S IN MY NAME.

18:35.536 --> 18:38.605
AND I FOUND SOMETHING
ELSE OUT TODAY.

18:38.605 --> 18:42.475
THE ONLY REASON
I'M TELLING YOU THIS

18:42.475 --> 18:46.547
IS BECAUSE I DON'T WANT YOU TO
FIND OUT LATER ON AND GET UPSET.

18:46.547 --> 18:48.882
WHAT IS IT?

18:48.882 --> 18:51.718
MY HOUSE IS BOUGHT
AND PAID FOR, TOO, IN CASH.

18:51.718 --> 18:56.289
WHO HELPED YOU FIND THAT OUT?
YOUR SLIMY, HO‐ISH LAWYER?

18:56.289 --> 18:57.991
NO.

18:57.991 --> 18:59.893
THEN HOW'D YOU FIND IT OUT?

18:59.893 --> 19:01.301
BECAUSE I WENT DOWN
TO THE COURTHOUSE

19:01.301 --> 19:04.337
AND SEARCHED THE DEEDS
BY MYSELF.

19:04.337 --> 19:05.839
AND THEY'RE LEGIT.

19:05.839 --> 19:07.841
SHE BOUGHT HER HOUSE.

19:07.841 --> 19:09.810
SHE'S BOUGHT MY HOUSE
AND THE TWO YARD.

19:09.810 --> 19:14.380
HOW IN THE HELL DID SHE GET
THAT KIND OF MONEY, BENJAMIN?

19:14.380 --> 19:15.816
I DON'T KNOW.

19:15.816 --> 19:18.585
BUT HOWEVER SHE GOT IT,
IT'S BOUGHT, AND IT'S PAID FOR.

19:18.585 --> 19:21.588
SO YOU NEED TO COME
TO THE HOUSE.

19:21.588 --> 19:22.889
I AIN'T STEPPING FOOT
IN THAT HOUSE

19:22.889 --> 19:25.225
UNTIL SHE TELLS ME
HOW SHE GOT THE MONEY.

19:25.225 --> 19:26.459
WHAT IF SHE DIDN'T
GET IT LEGIT?

19:26.459 --> 19:28.128
WELL, WE KNOW THAT.

19:28.128 --> 19:33.734
BUT WHAT I WANT TO KNOW IS
HOW MUCH BLOOD IS ON THAT MONEY.

19:33.734 --> 19:35.869
LOOK, MOM.
WE GOT TO THINK ABOUT THIS.

19:35.869 --> 19:36.903
THE HOUSE IS PAID FOR.

19:36.903 --> 19:38.338
AND YOU DON'T GOT NOWHERE
TO STAY.

19:38.338 --> 19:40.273
SO COME ON.

19:40.273 --> 19:42.976
UNTIL SHE TELLS ME,
I'M NOT COMING TO THAT HOUSE.

19:42.976 --> 19:44.645
WELL, I'LL GET HER
TO TELL ME.

19:44.645 --> 19:48.582
ALL YOU'RE GONNA GET HER TO DO
IS TELL YOU ANOTHER LIE.

19:48.582 --> 19:51.151
SHE'LL TELL ME.

19:51.151 --> 19:52.586
WHEN WILL YOU LEARN
THAT THAT GIRL

19:52.586 --> 19:54.721
IS NEVER
GONNA TELL YOU THE TRUTH?

19:54.721 --> 19:55.889
SHE'S NOT.

19:55.889 --> 19:57.724
I'LL GET HER.

19:57.724 --> 20:00.160
OKAY, AND WHEN I DO,
COME TO THE HOUSE?

20:00.160 --> 20:02.268
NO, SIR.

20:02.268 --> 20:04.070
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
WHY? WHAT?

20:04.070 --> 20:07.040
I NEED TO BE THERE
WHEN SHE TELLS YOU.

20:07.040 --> 20:09.075
OKAY.

20:09.075 --> 20:10.777
OKAY.

20:10.777 --> 20:12.445
AND THEN,
YOU'LL COME TO THE HOUSE?

20:12.445 --> 20:14.280
THAT'S SOMETHING I'M NEVER
GONNA HAVE TO WORRY ABOUT

20:14.280 --> 20:17.483
'CAUSE YOU WILL NEVER
KNOW THE TRUTH.

20:17.483 --> 20:20.887
NOW, GET OUT OF HERE.
‐OKAY.

20:20.887 --> 20:25.659
WELL, UH, I'M GONNA
COME BACK HERE LATER AND, UH,

20:25.659 --> 20:26.860
SIT DOWN AND HAVE A TALK.

20:26.860 --> 20:28.595
YEAH, OKAY.

20:30.597 --> 20:32.065
I LOVE YOU.

20:32.065 --> 20:34.234
MM‐HMM.

20:34.234 --> 20:36.302
BYE, BENJAMIN.

20:36.302 --> 20:39.906
WHAT IF SOMETHING
HAPPENS TO ME OUT THERE?

20:39.906 --> 20:41.307
YOU DON'T WANT TO TELL ME
YOU LOVE ME?

20:41.307 --> 20:44.144
YOU KNOW I LOVE YOU.

20:44.144 --> 20:45.612
BUT I AM STILL MAD AT YOU.

20:45.612 --> 20:48.281
RIGHT NOW, I AIN'T GOT NOTHING
FOR YOU.

20:48.281 --> 20:50.383
BYE.
‐ALL RIGHT.

20:50.383 --> 20:53.620
WELL, UH...
[ SIGHS ]

20:53.620 --> 20:55.388
I'M GONNA COME GET YOU
TOMORROW.

20:58.024 --> 20:59.993
♪♪♪♪

21:29.963 --> 21:32.766
WHAT TIME IS IT?

21:32.766 --> 21:34.535
I DON'T KNOW.

21:37.370 --> 21:41.474
NEVER BEEN LOCKED UP
BEFORE.

21:41.474 --> 21:43.510
PRISON.

21:43.510 --> 21:46.046
IT'S JAIL, NOT PRISON.

21:46.046 --> 21:48.048
WHAT'S THE DIFFERENCE?

21:48.048 --> 21:50.350
PRISON IS MUCH WORSE.

21:50.350 --> 21:53.654
LIKE THAT PLACE
WYATT WAS IN?

21:53.654 --> 21:55.421
YEP.

21:56.389 --> 21:58.559
[ SIGHS ]

21:58.559 --> 22:02.468
JIM WAS SO SURE

22:02.468 --> 22:05.806
PUTTING WYATT IN THERE
WOULD SCARE HIM STRAIGHT.

22:05.806 --> 22:08.308
IT SEEMS TO HAVE
MADE HIM WORSE.

22:08.308 --> 22:11.978
YEAH.

22:11.978 --> 22:15.181
I DON'T UNDERSTAND IT.

22:15.181 --> 22:16.282
I LOOKED AT MY BOY'S EYES.

22:16.282 --> 22:19.152
HE WAS BEGGING TO COME HOME ‐‐
BEGGING.

22:19.152 --> 22:21.287
I KNEW HE WOULDN'T MAKE IT
IN THERE.

22:21.287 --> 22:22.723
I THOUGHT HE'D GET
HIS WHOLE CONFESSION THING

22:22.723 --> 22:23.857
OUT OF HIS HEAD.

22:23.857 --> 22:25.992
HOW COULD YOU BE SO SURE?

22:25.992 --> 22:28.428
WE HAD HIM, VERONICA.

22:28.428 --> 22:30.931
HE HAD GIVEN UP.

22:30.931 --> 22:34.768
I DO NOT KNOW WHAT HAS HAPPENED
TO HIM TO MAKE HIM THIS ANGRY.

22:34.768 --> 22:40.941
WELL, PRISON
CAN BE A ROUGH PLACE.

22:40.941 --> 22:42.943
IS IT TRUE?

22:42.943 --> 22:45.712
WHAT?

22:45.712 --> 22:50.350
MEN ARE VIOLATED IN THERE?

22:50.350 --> 22:52.519
RAPED?

22:52.519 --> 22:55.121
YEP.

22:55.121 --> 22:57.624
BY OTHER INMATES?

22:57.624 --> 23:00.226
YES, KATHERYN.
IT'S TRUE.

23:00.226 --> 23:03.670
AREN'T THEY SUPPOSED
TO BE GUARDED BY GUARDS?

23:03.670 --> 23:05.539
THAT'S NOT ALWAYS ENOUGH.

23:09.876 --> 23:13.079
YOU DON'T THINK SOMETHING
HAPPENED TO HIM IN THERE.

23:13.079 --> 23:14.981
KATHERYN.

23:14.981 --> 23:17.083
MAYBE SOMEBODY GOT TO HIM.

23:17.083 --> 23:19.986
NOW, HOW COULD THEY DO THAT?

23:19.986 --> 23:23.189
YOU'RE RIGHT.
JIM WOULD NEVER ALLOW THAT.

23:23.189 --> 23:26.660
HE HAD HIM
MONITORED EVERY SECOND.

23:26.660 --> 23:28.662
YES.

23:28.662 --> 23:30.463
I'M SURE HE DID.

23:30.463 --> 23:36.737
IT'S JUST THAT I JUST CAN'T HELP
BUT THINK IT JUST...

23:36.737 --> 23:39.205
WHEN THEY CAME HOME
THAT SUMMER,

23:39.205 --> 23:42.375
I KNEW SOMETHING WAS WRONG.

23:42.375 --> 23:44.244
HE WAS JUST SO ANGRY.

23:49.315 --> 23:51.818
WAIT.

23:51.818 --> 23:53.720
THAT'S IT.
‐WHAT?

23:53.720 --> 23:57.591
‐SOMETHING DID HAPPEN TO HIM.
‐KATHERYN.

23:57.591 --> 23:59.526
NO.

23:59.526 --> 24:04.004
THEY CAME HOME FROM CAMP
THAT SUMMER, HE WAS ANGRY,

24:04.004 --> 24:06.607
AND HE HATED US.

24:06.607 --> 24:08.742
SOMETHING DID HAPPEN TO HIM.

24:08.742 --> 24:11.512
SOMETHING DID,
AND I NEED TO TELL JIM.

24:11.512 --> 24:13.747
YOU THINK THAT'S WISE?

24:13.747 --> 24:17.851
HE LET MY DAUGHTER DIE,
VERONICA.

24:17.851 --> 24:22.088
IF I FIND OUT THAT HE LET
SOMETHING HAPPEN TO WYATT

24:22.088 --> 24:26.259
WHILE HE WAS SUPPOSED
TO BE LOOKING OUT FOR HIM,

24:26.259 --> 24:32.298
HEAVEN HELP THAT MAN BECAUSE
I DO NOT KNOW WHAT I WILL DO.

24:32.298 --> 24:34.467
WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY THAT?

24:34.467 --> 24:36.803
YOU KNOW ME, VERONICA.

24:36.803 --> 24:38.171
YOU KNOW ME.

24:38.171 --> 24:40.974
YES.

24:40.974 --> 24:42.609
AND YOU KNEW MY FATHER.

24:42.609 --> 24:45.211
HM. YES.

24:45.211 --> 24:49.149
HE WAS A VERY POWERFUL MAN.

24:49.149 --> 24:52.352
‐YES, HE WAS.
‐AND HE WAS RUTHLESS.

24:52.352 --> 24:56.557
I AM MY FATHER'S DAUGHTER.

24:56.557 --> 24:59.726
AND IF I FIND OUT
THAT ANYTHING ‐‐ ANYTHING ‐‐

24:59.726 --> 25:02.636
HAPPENED TO MY SON,
THERE WILL BE NO POWER

25:02.636 --> 25:06.406
ON THIS EARTH
THAT WILL ESCAPE MY WRATH.

25:06.406 --> 25:08.374
KATHERYN, YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE TO CALM DOWN.

25:08.374 --> 25:12.045
JUST LIKE THAT PRIEST.

25:12.045 --> 25:15.882
JUST DISAPPEARED.

25:15.882 --> 25:18.118
KATHERYN, YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE TO CALM DOWN, OKAY?

25:18.118 --> 25:19.219
JUST CALM DOWN.

25:19.219 --> 25:20.453
I'M SURE IT'S FINE.

25:20.453 --> 25:21.755
I'M SURE NOTHING HAPPENED.

25:21.755 --> 25:22.823
YOU CAN'T THINK LIKE THAT.

25:22.823 --> 25:24.791
AND DON'T GO
MENTIONING THAT TO JIM,

25:24.791 --> 25:27.393
GET HIM ALL WORKED UP, OKAY?

25:27.393 --> 25:29.295
HE'S GOING THROUGH ENOUGH.

25:29.295 --> 25:32.298
SO JUST LET IT GO.

25:32.298 --> 25:34.735
VERONICA,

25:34.735 --> 25:37.904
WHEN HAVE YOU EVER CARED
ABOUT WHAT JIM IS GOING THROUGH?

25:39.973 --> 25:41.975
WHERE IS THAT PHONE CALL?

25:56.489 --> 25:57.758
[ SIGHS ]

26:06.873 --> 26:09.342
[ ROCK MUSIC PLAYS ]

26:35.035 --> 26:37.538
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

26:43.009 --> 26:45.078
HOW MUCH LONGER, MAN?

26:45.078 --> 26:46.479
WHAT?

26:46.479 --> 26:48.081
Who is this?

26:48.081 --> 26:50.250
‐IT'S JEFFERY.
‐OH, HEY.

26:50.250 --> 26:51.652
Hey.

26:51.652 --> 26:53.019
HEY, WE'VE BEEN
TRYING TO REACH YOU.

26:53.019 --> 26:54.988
WE?
WHAT ‐‐ WHO?

26:54.988 --> 26:56.156
ME AND THE D. A., MAN.

26:56.156 --> 26:57.624
D.A.?

26:57.624 --> 26:59.192
WHY IS THE D. A. CALLING ME?

26:59.192 --> 27:02.969
‐FOR THE DEAL.
‐What deal?

27:02.969 --> 27:04.705
YOU KNOW, MAN, HIT‐AND‐RUN.

27:04.705 --> 27:06.907
I TOLD YOU.
SHE GAVE US IMMUNITY.

27:06.907 --> 27:08.575
OH.

27:08.575 --> 27:11.845
YEAH, UM, OKAY.

27:11.845 --> 27:13.413
All right.
I mean, that's cool.

27:13.413 --> 27:14.948
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?

27:14.948 --> 27:17.417
UH, NOTHING.
I'M ‐‐ ARE ‐‐ ARE YOU HOME?

27:17.417 --> 27:18.552
Why?

27:18.552 --> 27:19.686
BECAUSE I'M ‐‐
I'M COMING OVER.

27:19.686 --> 27:21.555
I'M ON MY WAY.
‐WHY?

27:21.555 --> 27:24.324
Look, I need to talk to you
about something?

27:24.324 --> 27:25.792
I'M HAVING COMPANY.

27:25.792 --> 27:29.062
OH, GREAT, GOOD FOR YOU.

27:29.062 --> 27:30.463
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?

27:30.463 --> 27:31.598
NOTHING.
I'M JUST...

27:31.598 --> 27:32.933
LISTEN, I ‐‐ I JUST...

27:32.933 --> 27:35.569
NO. YOU SOUND STRANGE.

27:35.569 --> 27:37.938
STRANGE?
I SOUND STRANGE?

27:37.938 --> 27:39.573
YOU DRINKING?

27:39.573 --> 27:41.742
YES,
I'VE BEEN DRINKING, OKAY?

27:41.742 --> 27:43.443
I JUST...
‐Jeffery.

27:43.443 --> 27:45.478
‐What?
‐YOU DRINKING AND DRIVING?

27:45.478 --> 27:47.981
JUST, WYATT,
JUST, PLEASE, JUST LISTEN.

27:47.981 --> 27:50.651
This is serious.
‐WHAT'S GOING ON?

27:50.651 --> 27:53.186
‐LOOK, I'M ON MY WAY.
‐NO.

27:53.186 --> 27:54.487
Why not?

27:54.487 --> 27:56.389
BECAUSE I TOLD YOU,
I'M GOING TO HAVE COMPANY.

27:56.389 --> 27:57.558
YEAH.
YOU TOLD ME THAT ALREADY.

27:57.558 --> 27:59.826
I'M COMING OVER.
‐FINE.

27:59.826 --> 28:03.770
YOU DON'T GET TO WATCH.
I KNOW YOU.

28:03.770 --> 28:05.405
[ LAUGHS ]

28:07.407 --> 28:09.342
IDIOT.

28:11.545 --> 28:13.013
I KNOW YOU.

28:23.123 --> 28:25.225
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

28:26.627 --> 28:29.195
[ GEARS GRINDING,
TIRES SCREECHING ]

28:48.181 --> 28:49.249
GENTLEMEN.

28:49.249 --> 28:50.651
SO, YOU HAVE US IN HERE.

28:50.651 --> 28:52.218
AND YOU WON'T ALLOW
US TO MAKE A PHONE CALL.

28:52.218 --> 28:54.521
‐NO, WE'RE WORKING ‐‐
‐YOU'RE WORKING ON IT.

28:54.521 --> 28:56.657
FUNNY, THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT
YOUR PEOPLE HAVE BEEN SAYING.

28:56.657 --> 28:59.560
‐YES, I KNOW.
‐WHAT DO YOU WANT, JENNIFER?

28:59.560 --> 29:01.367
TO TALK TO JUDGE HARRINGTON.

29:03.336 --> 29:05.639
REGARDING?

29:05.639 --> 29:07.608
COME WITH ME.

29:07.608 --> 29:08.809
WON'T WORK.

29:08.809 --> 29:10.076
WHAT WON'T WORK?

29:10.076 --> 29:12.145
YOU'RE GOING TO OFFER ME
A DEAL.

29:12.145 --> 29:14.480
IT WON'T WORK.

29:14.480 --> 29:17.618
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT THE OFFER IS.

29:17.618 --> 29:19.953
YES, I DO.

29:19.953 --> 29:23.223
SO, YOU'RE GONNA OFFER DAVID
A DEAL AGAINST ME.

29:23.223 --> 29:25.158
WHAT'S THE MATTER, JENNIFER?

29:25.158 --> 29:26.993
ARE YOU SUDDENLY AFRAID
YOU'RE GONNA LOSE YOUR CASE

29:26.993 --> 29:28.161
AND YOUR JOB BOTH?

29:28.161 --> 29:29.963
NO, BUT YOU SHOULD BE LOOKING
FOR ANOTHER JOB

29:29.963 --> 29:31.965
BECAUSE IT'S OBVIOUS
THE GOVERNOR'S MANSION

29:31.965 --> 29:33.834
IS NOT HAPPENING.

29:33.834 --> 29:35.335
OH, I WOULDN'T BE SO SURE
ABOUT THAT.

29:35.335 --> 29:36.369
OH, JIM, PLEASE.

29:36.369 --> 29:38.404
IN THIS TOWN,
YOUR NAME IS LOWER

29:38.404 --> 29:41.141
THAN WHAT'S FLUSHED
IN THAT TOILET OVER THERE.

29:41.141 --> 29:42.843
OW.

29:42.843 --> 29:46.613
MR. HARRINGTON,
COME WITH ME, PLEASE.

29:46.613 --> 29:50.283
YOU'RE WASTING YOUR TIME.

29:50.283 --> 29:52.719
WELL, LET'S SEE.

29:52.719 --> 29:54.487
OFFICER.

30:08.642 --> 30:10.143
[ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]

30:39.506 --> 30:41.675
NOW, YOU KNOW THIS IS UGLY,
RIGHT?

30:41.675 --> 30:44.711
I AM NOT TALKING TO YOU
ABOUT JIM.

30:44.711 --> 30:47.648
COME ON, DAVID.
I KNOW YOU.

30:47.648 --> 30:49.015
YEAH.

30:49.015 --> 30:50.851
I KNOW YOU DO.

30:50.851 --> 30:52.686
AND I KNOW
YOU'RE SMARTER THAN THIS.

30:52.686 --> 30:55.856
I'M SMARTER THAN TALKING TO YOU
ABOUT THIS.

30:55.856 --> 30:57.323
HE'S GOING DOWN.

30:57.323 --> 31:00.861
ARE YOU WILLING TO CRASH
AND BURN WITH HIM?

31:00.861 --> 31:02.603
YOU ARE QUITE SURE
OF YOURSELF.

31:02.603 --> 31:04.270
I'M SURE ABOUT THIS.

31:04.270 --> 31:06.673
YOU ARE LIKE A DOG
WITH A BONE.

31:06.673 --> 31:09.009
YOU JUST WON'T LET GO,
WILL YOU?

31:09.009 --> 31:12.178
NOT UNTIL I GET
A BIGGER BONE.

31:12.178 --> 31:13.980
JENNIFER.

31:13.980 --> 31:17.618
‐I MISS YOU.
‐DON'T.

31:17.618 --> 31:19.953
I AM NOT GIVING JIM UP.

31:19.953 --> 31:23.356
DON'T MAKE THIS ANY HARDER ON ME
THAN IT HAS TO BE, PLEASE.

31:23.356 --> 31:26.026
I HAVE ALREADY TOLD YOU.

31:26.026 --> 31:29.295
JUST TESTIFY AGAINST HIM.

31:29.295 --> 31:30.564
AND YOU WILL BE FREE,

31:30.564 --> 31:35.101
FREE TO GO ON WITH YOUR LIFE,
COMPLETE IMMUNITY.

31:35.101 --> 31:38.271
IMMUNITY FOR ME
AND MY WIFE.

31:38.271 --> 31:42.609
NO, JUST FOR YOU.

31:42.609 --> 31:43.744
JENNIFER.

31:43.744 --> 31:46.980
YEAH, YOU KNOW
I CAN'T STAND THAT BITCH.

31:46.980 --> 31:50.584
I WAS SO TEMPTED
TO TELL HER ASS.

31:50.584 --> 31:51.852
NO. ENOUGH. STOP IT.

31:56.389 --> 31:59.492
DON'T MAKE
ME DO THIS TO YOU, PLEASE.

31:59.492 --> 32:01.034
JENNIFER.

32:01.034 --> 32:03.570
YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THIS.

32:05.539 --> 32:07.841
OKAY.

32:07.841 --> 32:11.044
I WILL LET HER WALK.

32:11.044 --> 32:13.580
BUT YOU GIVE ME JIM CRYER.

32:13.580 --> 32:17.183
SO THE DEAL
IS FOR ME AND VERONICA?

32:19.452 --> 32:22.155
YES.

32:22.155 --> 32:23.423
NO.

32:23.423 --> 32:25.125
DAVID.

32:25.125 --> 32:29.062
NO, NO, NO.
I ‐‐ I CAN'T DO THIS.

32:29.062 --> 32:32.599
YOU ARE LOYAL TO A FAULT.

32:32.599 --> 32:34.935
WELL, I'M SORRY.

32:34.935 --> 32:37.638
SEE, THAT'S YOUR PROBLEM.

32:37.638 --> 32:41.474
ONCE YOU'RE COMMITTED,
YOU STAY COMMITTED,

32:41.474 --> 32:44.578
EVEN IF IT'S
TO THE WRONG PERSON.

32:44.578 --> 32:46.279
DON'T DO THIS.

32:46.279 --> 32:48.014
I KNEW.

32:48.014 --> 32:50.984
I KNEW WHEN I CAME TO YOUR HOUSE
THE NIGHT OF THE FIRE,

32:50.984 --> 32:55.188
I KNEW
SHE TRIED TO HURT YOU.

32:55.188 --> 32:57.791
AND I WAS SO UPSET.

32:57.791 --> 32:58.992
ALL RIGHT, JENNIFER.

32:58.992 --> 33:02.035
I THINK YOU SHOULD TAKE ME BACK
TO MY CELL.

33:02.035 --> 33:04.037
I STILL LOVE YOU.

33:04.037 --> 33:06.339
AND I KNOW YOU STILL
LOVE ME, TOO.

33:06.339 --> 33:10.210
NO, JENNIFER, STOP.

33:10.210 --> 33:11.545
STOP IT, JENNIFER.

33:11.545 --> 33:14.881
JENNIFER, STOP IT.
‐PLEASE, DAVID, PLEASE, COME ON.

33:14.881 --> 33:17.751
STOP IT, JENNIFER.
STOP IT.

33:22.088 --> 33:24.591
YOU'VE NEVER BEEN THIS PERSON,
JENNIFER.

33:24.591 --> 33:27.427
YOU ARE NOT
THIS KIND OF WOMAN.

33:31.031 --> 33:32.966
[ SIGHS ]

33:41.407 --> 33:46.847
PLEASE, TAKE THE DEAL.

33:46.847 --> 33:49.516
I CAN'T.

33:53.954 --> 33:55.722
OKAY.

33:57.991 --> 34:00.293
THEN YOU LEAVE ME NO CHOICE.

34:00.293 --> 34:02.903
NONE.

34:02.903 --> 34:04.705
OKAY.

34:08.742 --> 34:10.544
OFFICER.

34:14.114 --> 34:15.949
GET HIM OUT OF HERE.

34:58.191 --> 35:01.034
SO, WHAT'S THE DEAL?

35:01.034 --> 35:03.970
FREEDOM
AND COMPLETE IMMUNITY.

35:03.970 --> 35:05.405
REALLY?

35:05.405 --> 35:07.073
YEAH.

35:07.073 --> 35:09.242
FOR JUST YOU?

35:09.242 --> 35:11.011
ME AND VERONICA.

35:13.246 --> 35:14.948
SHE IS REALLY AFTER ME.

35:14.948 --> 35:16.617
YES, SHE IS.

35:16.617 --> 35:18.752
AND YET YOU ARE STILL HERE.

35:18.752 --> 35:20.353
YES, I AM.

35:22.355 --> 35:24.558
SO YOU DIDN'T TAKE THE DEAL.

35:24.558 --> 35:25.659
WHAT?

35:25.659 --> 35:26.793
WHY NOT?

35:26.793 --> 35:28.461
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "WHY NOT"?

35:28.461 --> 35:29.996
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
WHAT DO I MEAN, WHY NOT?

35:29.996 --> 35:31.698
WHY DIDN'T YOU TAKE THE DEAL?
YOU COULD BURY ME.

35:31.698 --> 35:34.300
YOU COLD BE FREE AND CLEAR
AT THE SAME TIME, VERY SIMPLE.

35:34.300 --> 35:35.536
I'M NOT TRYING TO BURY YOU.

35:35.536 --> 35:37.571
THAT'S NOT WHAT FRIENDS DO.

35:37.571 --> 35:39.239
FRIENDS?

35:39.239 --> 35:41.708
YES, THAT'S WHAT WE ARE.
YOU KNOW THAT.

35:41.708 --> 35:43.276
THE ONLY THING I KNOW,
DAVID,

35:43.276 --> 35:45.445
IS THAT YOUR WIFE
TRIED TO DESTROY MY LIFE.

35:45.445 --> 35:49.049
WHAT MY WIFE MAY OR MAY NOT
HAVE DONE IS NOT ME.

35:49.049 --> 35:50.416
AND I RESENT YOU TREATING ME

35:50.416 --> 35:51.852
AS IF I HAVE HARMED YOU
IN SOME WAY.

35:51.852 --> 35:56.056
I HAVE BEEN NOTHING
BUT A FRIEND TO YOU, JIM.

35:56.056 --> 36:00.661
I'VE KEPT YOUR DIRTY SECRETS
AND EVEN HELPED BURY SOME.

36:00.661 --> 36:04.337
AND I WILL NOT ALLOW
YOU TO TREAT ME THIS WAY.

36:04.337 --> 36:05.906
YOU'RE RIGHT.
I'M SORRY.

36:06.039 --> 36:08.542
OKAY.

36:08.542 --> 36:10.410
IT'S JUST EVER SINCE AMANDA
DIED, I CAN'T SEEM TO...

36:10.410 --> 36:12.846
I KNOW YOU ARE GOING
THROUGH HELL.

36:15.381 --> 36:17.684
I'M NOT EVEN HERE, DAVID,
IN THIS ROOM.

36:17.684 --> 36:20.453
I FEEL LIKE I'M FLOATING AROUND
LOOKING DOWN AT EVERYTHING.

36:20.453 --> 36:23.489
I ‐‐ I ‐‐ I CAN'T FEEL.
I MAKE DECISIONS.

36:23.489 --> 36:26.693
I DON'T RECALL
WHAT THE HELL THEY ARE.

36:26.693 --> 36:29.863
ALL I CAN SEE IS MY LITTLE
GIRL'S FACE IN THAT BODY BAG.

36:29.863 --> 36:33.066
‐JIM.
‐YEAH?

36:33.066 --> 36:38.639
I NEED TO KNOW ‐‐
HAVE YOU SET UP SOMETHING?

36:38.639 --> 36:40.373
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

36:40.373 --> 36:41.775
MY WIFE.

36:41.775 --> 36:44.310
UH, NO, NO.

36:44.310 --> 36:47.413
ARE YOU SURE?

36:47.413 --> 36:49.149
YEAH.

36:49.149 --> 36:51.117
SO WHAT ARE YOU PLANNING?

36:51.117 --> 36:52.919
‐WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
‐I KNOW YOU.

36:52.919 --> 36:54.788
YOU ALWAYS HAVE A PLAN
TO GET EVEN.

36:54.788 --> 36:57.223
OH, NO, NO, NO.
DAVID, NOT THIS TIME.

36:57.223 --> 36:58.759
WHAT'S SO DIFFERENT
ABOUT THIS TIME?

36:58.759 --> 37:02.035
AMANDA IS DIFFERENT
ABOUT THIS TIME.

37:02.035 --> 37:04.103
I'M SORRY,
DAVID, YOU STOOD WITH ME.

37:04.103 --> 37:06.573
AND I'VE BEEN AGAINST YOU,
AND I APOLOGIZE.

37:06.573 --> 37:07.974
OKAY.

37:10.409 --> 37:11.945
I LOVE YOU, DAVID.

37:11.945 --> 37:13.112
WE'VE BEEN
THROUGH TOO MUCH TOGETHER.

37:13.112 --> 37:15.481
YOU KNOW THAT, RIGHT?
‐YES, WE HAVE.

37:15.481 --> 37:18.017
SO I NEED TO ASK YOU
TO PROMISE ME SOMETHING.

37:18.017 --> 37:21.154
WHAT'S THAT?

37:21.154 --> 37:23.389
I NEED YOU TO PROMISE ME
THAT YOU WILL PUNISH YOUR WIFE

37:23.389 --> 37:25.125
FOR WHAT SHE'S DONE.

37:25.125 --> 37:26.259
PUNISH HER?

37:26.259 --> 37:29.563
DAVID, I HAVEN'T DONE ANYTHING.
NOTHING.

37:29.563 --> 37:33.199
SO I NEED YOU TO PROMISE ME
THAT YOU WILL DO IT FOR ME.

37:33.199 --> 37:35.936
‐SHE IS MY WIFE.
‐YES.

37:35.936 --> 37:39.272
SO YOUR PUNISHMENT
WILL BE FAIR.
‐JIM.

37:39.272 --> 37:41.141
DAVID, SOMETIMES,
WE HAVE TO PUNISH THE PEOPLE

37:41.141 --> 37:43.209
THAT WE LOVE SIMPLY
BECAUSE WE LOVE THEM.

37:43.209 --> 37:44.911
BELIEVE ME, IF I PUNISH HER,

37:44.911 --> 37:47.480
THERE WILL BE NO LOVE
INVOLVED WHATSOEVER.

37:47.480 --> 37:48.782
I DON'T NEED TO HEAR THAT.

37:48.782 --> 37:51.284
I NEED
TO HEAR YOU PROMISE ME

37:51.284 --> 37:54.688
THAT SHE WILL BE PUNISHED
FOR THIS.

37:54.688 --> 37:57.490
I WILL NOT ARGUE THIS
WITH YOU.

37:57.490 --> 37:59.092
ARE YOU SURE?

37:59.092 --> 38:01.201
AND YOU WILL NOT HARM
MY WIFE.

38:01.201 --> 38:03.570
ARE YOU SURE?

38:03.570 --> 38:05.772
I'M GONNA HAND YOU
THIS OLIVE BRANCH

38:05.772 --> 38:08.909
ONE TIME, DAVID ‐‐
ONE TIME.

38:08.909 --> 38:11.411
YOU SHOULD TAKE IT.

38:11.411 --> 38:17.050
I WILL DEAL WITH MY WIFE
AS I SEE FIT.

38:17.050 --> 38:18.852
OKAY.

38:37.103 --> 38:39.239
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

39:02.769 --> 39:05.606
LICENSE AND REGISTRATION.

39:05.606 --> 39:08.775
I ‐‐ I ‐‐ I ACTUALLY
DON'T HAVE IT RIGHT NOW.

39:08.775 --> 39:12.212
‐IS THIS YOUR CAR?
‐N‐NO, SIR.

39:12.212 --> 39:14.615
WHOSE CAR IS IT?

39:14.615 --> 39:17.483
‐UH, A FRIEND'S.
‐OUT OF THE CAR.

39:27.628 --> 39:29.796
YOU BEEN DRINKING?
‐NO.

39:29.796 --> 39:32.332
I CAN SMELL IT FROM HERE.

39:32.332 --> 39:33.466
UH...

39:33.466 --> 39:34.500
YOU BURNT THIS CLUTCH UP.

39:34.500 --> 39:37.003
I CAN SMELL THAT, TOO.

39:37.003 --> 39:40.807
‐DID I‐‐
‐WHERE WERE YOU GOING?

39:40.807 --> 39:42.442
UH, A HOME. I...

39:42.442 --> 39:45.912
WHY'D YOU LEAVE YOUR FRIEND
SO QUICKLY?

39:45.912 --> 39:47.614
I DON'T ‐‐ I WAS ‐‐
I WAS TIRED.

39:47.614 --> 39:50.784
‐I ‐‐ I DON'T...
‐YOU'RE DRUNK.

39:50.784 --> 39:52.485
HOLD OUT YOUR ARMS.

39:52.485 --> 39:55.221
HOLD YOUR HEAD BACK.

39:55.221 --> 39:56.422
CLOSE YOUR EYES.
TOUCH YOUR NOSE.

39:56.422 --> 39:59.192
HOLD OUT YOUR ARMS,
OUT THIS WAY.

39:59.192 --> 40:00.961
OKAY.

40:00.961 --> 40:02.836
CLOSE YOUR EYES.
TOUCH YOUR NOSE.

40:05.105 --> 40:06.372
ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.
‐NO.

40:06.372 --> 40:07.808
‐I'M TAKING YOU IN.
‐NO, PLEASE DON'T.

40:07.808 --> 40:09.543
PLEASE.

40:09.543 --> 40:13.514
THIS BLOOD ON YOUR SHIRT?

40:13.514 --> 40:15.448
NO. NO.

40:15.448 --> 40:16.883
NO. IT'S ‐‐

40:16.883 --> 40:18.819
LET'S GO.

40:18.819 --> 40:20.587
PLEASE, PLEASE.

40:39.773 --> 40:41.107
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

41:27.894 --> 41:30.196
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:30.196 --> 41:31.932
STEP OUT. I GOT TO CHECK YOU
BEFORE I TAKE YOU IN.

41:31.932 --> 41:33.199
YOU KNOW,
SHE TOLD ME YOU WERE GAY.

41:33.199 --> 41:35.435
THIS IS FOR THE SON.
HE HAS A TRUST FUND.

41:35.435 --> 41:36.469
AND YOU WANT ME TO GIVE IT
TO HIM?

41:36.469 --> 41:37.804
HE'S A RESPONSIBLE KID.

41:37.804 --> 41:39.305
HE WON'T GO NEAR ANY DRUGS.

41:39.305 --> 41:40.541
YOU TOLD ME
YOU HAD NO MONEY.

41:40.541 --> 41:42.475
THIS PLACE GOES
FOR OVER 500 G's?

41:42.475 --> 41:44.044
‐SHE BOUGHT ME THE PLACE AND ‐‐
‐WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

41:44.044 --> 41:45.646
KING, SHE BOUGHT ALL THIS.

41:45.646 --> 41:47.180
QUINCY JR. CAN'T GET A HOTEL.

41:47.180 --> 41:48.515
IT'S NOT A STABLE PLACE.

41:48.515 --> 41:50.283
I HAVE TO TAKE MY MEDICINE.

41:50.283 --> 41:52.318
THEY DIDN'T SAY
YOU HAD ANY MEDICINE.

41:52.318 --> 41:55.355
FIND THIS NEWSPAPER AND MAKE
SURE TO GET A COPY OF IT.

41:55.355 --> 41:57.390
VERONICA,
ARE YOU HAVING AN AFFAIR?
